## Non-Negotiable Standards

- **UK English** — all labels, placeholder text, error messages, and aria labels
- **Reactive Forms only** — use `FormBuilder` + `FormGroup`; no template-driven forms for complex screens
- **JWT + MSAL** — always attach tokens via the HTTP interceptor; never hand-roll token attachment in services
- **Route guards** — every protected route must have `AuthGuard` and the appropriate `RoleGuard` / `ModuleAccessGuard`
- **Signals** — prefer Angular signals (`signal()`, `computed()`, `effect()`) over manual RxJS `BehaviorSubject` for local state
- **Desktop-first** responsive layout; WCAG AA accessibility on all interactive elements
